Step-4 Create dimension and Fact Tables in ColaberryResortRealtyDM Database 4

Download the Code File provided below

Run that code into SQL Server Management Studio to create Dimension and Fact Tables in ColaberryResortRealtyDM database .



Refresh the Database to see that Tables have been created in the database


We can see that Tables are created in ColaberryResortRealtyDM but there is no data into it.
